md:
giải nghĩa từ "wee" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

* Wee: (từ loại: adjective)
	+ Meaning: small, tiny, little
	+ Example sentence: "The wee kitten curled up on my lap."
	+ Related words: small, tiny, little, miniature, diminutive

* Wee: (từ loại: noun)
	+ Meaning: a small amount of urine
	+ Example sentence: "I had a wee accident on the way to the bathroom."
	+ Related words: pee, urine, toilet, bathroom

* Wee: (từ loại: adverb)
	+ Meaning: very early in the morning
	+ Example sentence: "I woke up wee hours of the morning to start my project."
	+ Related words: early, morning, dawn, sunrise

Note: The word "wee" can have different meanings depending on the context and region. The above explanations are some of the common meanings of "wee".
